      <title>数学笔记</title>
      <link href="/2019/04/26/math/"/>
      <url>/2019/04/26/math/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="统计学"><a href="#统计学" class="headerlink" title="统计学"></a>统计学</h2><h3 id="均值"><a href="#均值" class="headerlink" title="均值"></a>均值</h3><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\bar{x}=\frac{\sum_{n=1}^Nx_n}{N}</script><h3 id="期望"><a href="#期望" class="headerlink" title="期望"></a>期望</h3><ol><li><p>离散型</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">{E(X)=\sum_{k=1}^\infty {x_k}{p_k}}</script></li><li><p>连续型 </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">E(X)=\int_{-\infty}^\infty xf(x)dx</script></li></ol><h3 id="方差"><a href="#方差" class="headerlink" title="方差"></a>方差</h3><ol><li><p>离散型</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">{D(X)=\sum_{k=1}^\infty [x_k-E(X)]^2 {p_k}}</script><p><center>或</center></p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">s^2=\frac{\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-\bar{X})^2}{n-1}</script></li><li><p>连续型  </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">{D(X)=\int_{-\infty}^\infty[x-E(X)]^2f(x)dx}</script><p><script type="math/tex">f(x)</script>为连续性随机变量X的概率密度函数</p></li></ol><h3 id="标准差"><a href="#标准差" class="headerlink" title="标准差"></a>标准差</h3><script type="math/tex; mode=display">s=\sqrt{\frac{\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-\bar{X})^2}{n-1}}</script><h3 id="协方差"><a href="#协方差" class="headerlink" title="协方差"></a>协方差</h3><script type="math/tex; mode=display">{Cov(X,Y)=E\{[X-E(X)][Y-E(Y)]\}}\\=E[XY]-E[X]E[Y]</script><h3 id="相关系数"><a href="#相关系数" class="headerlink" title="相关系数"></a>相关系数</h3><script type="math/tex; mode=display">{\rho_{XY}=\frac{Cov(X,Y)}{\sqrt{D(X)}\sqrt{D(Y)}}}</script><h2 id="资料来源"><a href="#资料来源" class="headerlink" title="资料来源"></a>资料来源</h2><p>百度百科<br><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%B9%E5%B7%AE/3108412?fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">方差</a><br><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%B7%AE/1415772?fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">标准差</a><br><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%95%B0/11031224?fromtitle=%E5%9D%87%E5%80%BC&amp;fromid=5922988" target="_blank" rel="noopener">平均数</a><br><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B/5362790?fromtitle=%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%9B&amp;fromid=10318906&amp;fr=aladdin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">数学期望</a></p><p>CSDN<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_25051779/article/details/51914534" target="_blank" rel="noopener">方差与协方差</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/sinat_25873421/article/details/80469530" target="_blank" rel="noopener">统计学理论基础 方差 &amp; 协方差 &amp; 标准差</a>  </p><h2 id="关于Mathjex"><a href="#关于Mathjex" class="headerlink" title="关于Mathjex"></a>关于Mathjex</h2><p>网上找了很多<a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-math" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo-math</a>的资料，但是屡试失败，最后用<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/68e6f82d88b7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo-renderer-kramed</a>引擎代替</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
