      <title>Hexo-admin添加云图片</title>
      <link href="/2019/04/17/cloudphoto/"/>
      <url>/2019/04/17/cloudphoto/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h2><p>在用hexo-admin后台写markdown的时候正想要加图片的时候，发现操作十分麻烦，需要用SFTP软件上传到指定位置，经过一轮的资料搜索，找到了几个方法。<br>1.<a href="https://github.com/lwz7512/hexo-admin-ehc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo-admin-ehc</a><br>2.<a href="https://github.com/xbotao/hexo-admin-qiniu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo-admin-qiniu</a> </p><p>但最后发现，ehc搞不定，qiniu需要实名注册。（其实是hexo-admin可以的，详见<a href="#solution3">方法三</a>）<br>依照这个思路，找到了另外两个解决方法：<br>1.使用<a href="https://cloudinary.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cloudinary</a>保存图片<br>2.建立<a href="http://www.github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github</a>项目用来保存图片<br>接下来本文会详细介绍这两个方法  </p><p>[2019-4-20更新]<br>发现了一个新的更快的方法，可直接跳到<a href="#solution3">方法三查看</a></p><h2 id="方法一-使用cloudinary保存图片"><a href="#方法一-使用cloudinary保存图片" class="headerlink" title="方法一.使用cloudinary保存图片"></a>方法一.使用cloudinary保存图片</h2><ol><li><p>进入<a href="https://cloudinary.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cloudinary</a>，点右上角注册<br><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555762874/hexo_james/cloudphoto/cloudinary1_srtv4b.png"></p></li><li><p>注册后进入，初始化设置（当然可以选择跳过）<br><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555763250/hexo_james/cloudphoto/cloudinary3_br1ur4.png"></p></li><li><p>建立hexo文件夹<br>点击左上角这个图标<br><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555764342/hexo_james/cloudphoto/cloudinary4_pqhn2a.png" width="75%"><br>点击新增文件夹，命名为hexo （实际上可以跳过这一步，不过有文件夹好管理一些）<br><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555765356/hexo_james/cloudphoto/cloudinary5_ermi0p.png"><br>然后拖拉图片上传<br>图片上传后，点击图片的左上角复制链接<br><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555765834/hexo_james/cloudphoto/cloudinary6_x3d1hz.bmp"></p><h3 id="效果"><a href="#效果" class="headerlink" title="效果"></a>效果</h3><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555509325/hexo_james/icon.jpg " width="25%" height="25%"></p><h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;(这里添上刚才复制的网址)https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555509325/hexo_james/icon.jpg&quot; width=&quot;25%&quot; height=&quot;25%&quot; /&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p><br></p><h2 id="方法二-建立github项目用来保存图片"><a href="#方法二-建立github项目用来保存图片" class="headerlink" title="方法二.建立github项目用来保存图片"></a>方法二.建立github项目用来保存图片</h2><p>既然cloudinary这类都可以，那github当然也不例外  </p><ol><li>建立github项目<br>用浏览器打开github项目,点击需要用的图片（怎么用github请自行百度）<figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555774984/hexo_james/cloudphoto/github_juiui6.png" alt title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure></li><li>获取图片地址<br>图片地址格式：<a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/用户名/项目名称/你的分支(默认master)/图片路径/图片名称" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/用户名/项目名称/你的分支(默认master)/图片路径/图片名称</a><br>所以我的图片地址是：<a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JamesHoi/hexo/master/icon.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JamesHoi/hexo/master/icon.jpg</a>  <h3 id="代码-1"><a href="#代码-1" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;(这里输入你的图片地址)https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JamesHoi/hexo/master/icon.jpg&quot; width=&quot;25%&quot; height=&quot;25%&quot;/&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p><br></p><h2 id="方法三-直接复制图片到hexo-admin"><a href="#方法三-直接复制图片到hexo-admin" class="headerlink" title="方法三.直接复制图片到hexo-admin"></a>方法三.直接复制图片到hexo-admin</h2><p>我发现原来我搞了这么多其实hexo-admin还是可以添加图片的，只是没有按钮  </p><ol><li>右键复制电脑中的图片</li><li>Ctrl+V复制在hexo-admin写markdown的位置<figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555779125/hexo_james/cloudphoto/hexo-admin-smaller_yvyfvw.png" alt title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure>图片会自动上传到 hexo项目路径/source/images/<br>更多设置详见 hexo-admin后台-Settings<figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jameshoi/image/upload/v1555779376/hexo_james/cloudphoto/hexo-admin-setting_jsa5du.png" alt title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption"></div>            </figure>不过我尝试此方法的时候，发现这个方法会令hexo-admin deploy后webhook无法<code>git pull</code><br>解决方法：在hexo-admin的deploy脚本中添加<code>git stash</code>命令<br>还有就是经常Ctrl+V没有反应，若此方法不行，请看<a href="#solution1">方法一</a>或<a href="#solution2">方法二</a></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>关于python的matplotlib库下实现按键后切换show图片</title>
      <link href="/2019/04/10/matplotlib-show/"/>
      <url>/2019/04/10/matplotlib-show/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>   最近在用pytorch做mnist库的手写识别，由于平时编程有点“强迫症”，想按一下Enter就显示对应的手写图片和识别出来的数字，而网上找到的matplotlib教程都最多只能暂停指定的秒数，不能等待键盘输入，从而做不到想要的效果</p><p>尝试了半个晚上，终于成功了，参考了<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/xiaodongxiexie/article/details/78195860" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/xiaodongxiexie/article/details/78195860</a></p><p>废话不多说，先上代码<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#Python 3.6.5 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#Skimage Library</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> skimage <span class="keyword">import</span> io</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">show</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">global</span> num</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(num&lt;<span class="number">60000</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        img=io.imread(<span class="string">'data/test/'</span>+str(num)+<span class="string">'.png'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        io.imshow(img)</span><br><span class="line">        plt.ion()</span><br><span class="line">        plt.pause(<span class="number">0.01</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        input(<span class="string">"Press Enter to Continue"</span>)<span class="comment">#之后改成识别输出</span></span><br><span class="line">        num+=<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>经过尝试，假如用plt.show的话会卡住这时一定要开另一个线程用plt.close关掉…<br>假如用plt.ion不会卡住，但一定要用plt.pause让窗口保留，然后用input等待键盘输入后才开始下一个循环</p><p>运行结果<br> <img src="https://img-blog.csdn.net/20180811020732107?watermark/2/text/aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2JhaWR1XzM4NjM1MTkw/font/5a6L5L2T/fontsize/400/fill/I0JBQkFCMA==/dissolve/70" width="60%"></p><p>原文网址: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/baidu_38635190/article/details/81572362" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/baidu_38635190/article/details/81572362</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
